-- Urbi to Hire Bain & Co., Boston Consulting to Improve Operations
-- B y   J o n a t h a n   J .   L e v i n
-- 2012-08-04T01:32:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-04/urbi-to-hire-bain-co-boston-consulting-to-improve-operations.html
Urbi Desarrollos Urbanos SAB,
 Mexico ’s third-largest homebuilder by sales, said it’s hiring
Bain & Co. and Boston Consulting Group Inc. to help it analyze
its business processes and portfolio.  The consulting companies are starting work with Urbi this
quarter, Selene Avalos, Urbi’s chief financial officer, said in
a telephone interview from Mexicali, Mexico. In addition to
evaluating its geographic presence, Urbi is also trying to
streamline its relationship with mortgage providers, she said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jonathan J. Levin in Mexico City at 
